sourcesContent: import React from "react"; import { Typography, Box, Button, Container, Grid, Card, CardContent } from "@mui/material"; const DashboardPage = () => { return ( {/* Hero Section */} Welcome to CautisCloud Decentralized Cloud Storage for Security and Privacy {/* About Section */} Why Choose CautisCloud? CautisCloud is a safe and secure cloud storage platform that prioritizes security, offering a seamless and intuitive experience for protecting your digital assets. Our assortive encryption and decentralized architecture ensures your data is always safe and accessible. {/* Features Section */} Key Features {/* File Splitting Feature */} File Splitting Your files are broken into smaller chunks for secure storage and distribution. {/* Node Distribution Feature */} Node Distribution Files are stored across multiple nodes, ensuring reliability and redundancy. {/* IPFS Hashing Feature */} IPFS Hashing Unique IPFS hashes ensure your data is tamper-proof and secure. {/* Call to Action */} Ready to get started with CautisCloud? ); }; export default DashboardPage;
